珍惜對方 成日諗可能係以前好多戰爭 科技唔發達<br />\n雙方先會珍惜感情 而又夠長久"},{"pid":"a9fb307858d25f74f4918656f26c894b9bd42ce0","tid":1003034,"uid":215061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"及時行樂啦，今日唔知聽日事，開心就得，冇話浪唔浪費時間，自己鐘意就得，生同死整定，所以好多野都係靠自己體會先至會發覺條路要點行，靠講未必會明白。。。"},{"pid":"ca76276a3a7c017f60b432e254fd9929ee6789bf","tid":1003034,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T22:33:49.000Z","msg":"人生第一堂課應該要學生同死；而學死要先於學生。"},{"pid":"4339110a6b7a8c17fd0fb48b66c35922e8158e84","tid":1003034,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T22:39:24.000Z","msg":"學 生好啲！<br />\n你個名都成日掛住屌閪架啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e39d1a46d5a55f3b1f205bb6e0c29d8e819dbd","tid":1003034,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T23:01:25.000Z","msg":"香港人好多都有信心自己未來30年都唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802ecaf813c2e6698a87551fac39d3c30fb177ff","tid":1003034,"uid":73024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4339110a6b7a8c17fd0fb48b66c35922e8158e84","tid":1003034,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T22:39:24.000Z","msg":"學 生好啲！<br />\n你個名都成日掛住屌閪架啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n及時行樂！"},{"pid":"6388a9c6fd4f0276ee1bbb5e6df5be4cb60a8732","tid":1003034,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <